{
	"info": {
		"name": "FlatFlow API",
		"description": "FlatFlow API - Flat management application with authentication, CQRS, and Clean Architecture.\n\n## Auth Flow\n1. Register a new user (POST /api/auth/register)\n2. Login to get JWT token (POST /api/auth/login)\n3. Use token in Authorization header: Bearer {{token}}\n\n## Enums\n- ChoreFrequency: 0 = Once, 1 = Daily, 2 = Weekly, 3 = Monthly\n- PaymentShareStatus: 0 = New, 1 = Partial, 2 = Paid",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
